snippet.title: The Rise and Fall of Siddharth Abhimanyu | Thani Oruvan - Back to Back Scenes | Jayam Ravi | Sun NXT
snippet.description:

Witness his rise as a brilliant and ruthless antagonist and the ultimate battle of wits with Jayam Ravi’s character. Featuring stunning performances by Nayanthara and a gripping storyline that keeps you hooked till the end. Watch Thani Oruvan now on Sun NXT to experience one of Tamil cinema’s finest action thrillers!

kn.title: ದಿ ಅಲ್ಟಿಮೇಟ್ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಚಾಲೆಂಜ್ (KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes)
kn.description:
KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes ಅಂತಿಮ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಸವಾಲನ್ನು ಎದುರಿಸಲು ಒಗ್ಗೂಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾರೆ! 


ಟೆಸ್ಟ್ ಸರಣಿಗೆ ಮೊದಲು, ಅವರು ಪ್ರತ್ಯೇಕವಾಗಿ ತಮ್ಮ ಶಕ್ತಿ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಖರತೆಯನ್ನು ಪರೀಕ್ಷಿಸುವ ವೈಯಕ್ತಿಕ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಸವಾಲುಗಳನ್ನು ಜಯಿಸಬೇಕು. 

 

ಈ ನಂತರ, ಅವರು ಸೇರಿ ಟ್ರಿಕ್ಕಿ ಬೌಲಿಂಗ್

hi.title: KL Rahul और Ben Stokes की सबसे कठिन बैटिंग चुनौती!
hi.description:
बेन स्टोक्स और के.एल. राहुल मिलकर क्रिकेट की अब तक की सबसे चुनौतीपूर्ण बैटिंग चैलेंज का सामना करने वाले हैं! 

आने वाली टेस्ट सीरीज़ से पहले, दोनों को अपनी-अपनी व्यक्तिगत क्रिकेट परीक्षाओं से गुजरना होगा — जहाँ उनकी सटीकता और ताकत की असली परख होगी। 

इसके बाद ही वे एक साथ मिलकर तेज़ तर्रार बॉलिंग मशीनों और तेजी से हिलते लक्ष्यों के खिलाफ एक रोमांचक "बॉस बैटल" में उतरेंगे।

snippet.title: Back to Back Comedy Scenes 😍🤣| Kick | Ravi Teja | Brahmanandam | Ilena | Ali | Telugu Comedy Scene
snippet.description:
Kick is a 2009 Indian Telugu-language action comedy film directed by Surender Reddy from a story by Vakkantham Vamsi. The film stars Ravi Teja, Ileana, and Shaam while Brahmanandam plays a supporting role. 

నైనా(ఇలియానా)కి పోలీస్ ఆఫీసర్ కళ్యాణ కృష్ణ(శ్యామ్)కి పెళ్ళి చూపులలో తన ప్రేమ కథని శ్యామ్ కి చెప్తుంది. ఆ కథలో కళ్యాణ్ (రవితేజ) చిన్నప్పటి నుంచీ కిక్..కిక్ అంటూ కలవరిస్తూంటాడు. అందుకుతగ్గట్లుగానే కిక్ ఇవ్వని ఏ పనీ చెయ్యడు...కిక్కు ఇస్తుందంటే ఎటువంటి పని చెయ్యటానికైనా వెనకాడడు..అంతేగాక కిక్ తగ్గిపోతే ఆ పనిలో కొనసాగటానికి ఇష్టపడడు. దాంతో ఏ ఉద్యోగంలోనూ వారం మించి పనిచేయడు. అలాంటి అతని విచిత్ర జీవితంలోకి ప్రతీది పెపఫెక్ట్ గా ఉండాలనుకునే ఇలియానా ప్రవేశిస్తుంది. అతని ఏటిట్యూడ్ చూసి మొదట ఆమె కసురుకున్నా తర్వాత ప్రేమలో పడుతుంది. పడిందే తడువుగా అతన్ని ఏదన్నా ఉద్యోగంలో చేరి సెటిల్ అవ్వమంటుంది.

localized.description:
Kick is a 2009 Indian Telugu-language action comedy film directed by Surender Reddy from a story by Vakkantham Vamsi. The film stars Ravi Teja, Ileana, and Shaam while Brahmanandam plays a supporting role. 

నైనా(ఇలియానా)కి పోలీస్ ఆఫీసర్ కళ్యాణ కృష్ణ(శ్యామ్)కి పెళ్ళి చూపులలో తన ప్రేమ కథని శ్యామ్ కి చెప్తుంది. ఆ కథలో కళ్యాణ్ (రవితేజ) చిన్నప్పటి నుంచీ కిక్..కిక్ అంటూ కలవరిస్తూంటాడు. అందుకుతగ్గట్లుగానే కిక్ ఇవ్వని ఏ పనీ చెయ్యడు...కిక్కు ఇస్తుందంటే ఎటువంటి పని చెయ్యటానికైనా వెనకాడడు..అంతేగాక కిక్ తగ్గిపోతే ఆ పనిలో కొనసాగటానికి ఇష్టపడడు. దాంతో ఏ ఉద్యోగంలోనూ వారం మించి పనిచేయడు. అలాంటి అతని విచిత్ర జీవితంలోకి ప్రతీది పెపఫెక్ట్ గా ఉండాలనుకునే ఇలియానా ప్రవేశిస్తుంది. అతని ఏటిట్యూడ్ చూసి మొదట ఆమె కసురుకున్నా తర్వాత ప్రేమలో పడుతుంది. పడిందే తడువుగా అతన్ని ఏదన్నా ఉద్యోగంలో చేరి సెటిల్ అవ్వమంటుంది.

ko.title: 마인크래프트 스피드러너 vs 10만 달러 현상금 사냥꾼
ko.description:
다콰비스 VS 드림 결승전. 정말 최고였어요!

$7,000 메달 경연 대회 참가 신청: https://pages.medal.tv/dream

제 소셜 미디어 팔로우:
➽ 트위터 - @dream
➽ 인스타그램 - @dreamwastaken
➽ 스냅챗 - @dreampublic

상품: https://www.dreams.is

다콰비스: ​⁠@DaquavisMC

이 시리즈의 이름을 '마인크래프트 맨헌트'로 정했습니다. 이 영상은 마인크래프트 맨헌트의 다른 버전인데, 한 명의 헌터가 10만 달러를 걸고 싸우는 내용입니다.

$10만 챌린지의 세 번째이자 마지막 결투입니다. 승패를 가르는 경기입니다.

새로운 마인크래프트 버전 1.16 챌린지인데, 이번에 도전해 보기로 했습니다. 저는 게임에서 이기기 위해 노력하는 반면, 다콰비스는 저를 막으려 합니다. 마치 경주처럼 치열하고, 정말 많은 것이 걸려 있습니다.

마인크래프트는 아니지만, 워터 라이즈(Water Rises)나 마인크래프트지만 라바 라이즈(Lava Rises) 같은 챌린지 말고 다른 것도 괜찮습니다. 이건 킬러/암살자를 상대로 하는 마인크래프트 스피드런/스피드러너 게임입니다.

#마인크래프트맨헌트

ja.title: マインクラフト スピードランナー VS 10万ドルの賞金稼ぎ
ja.description:
Daquavis VS Dreamの最終決戦。これは本当に最高でした。

$7,000メダルコンテストへの参加はこちら：https://pages.medal.tv/dream

Daquavis: ​⁠@DaquavisMC

このシリーズは「Minecraft Manhunt」と名付けることにしました。この動画は、ハンターが1人で賞金10万ドルを賭けた、少し変わったバージョンです。

これは、10万ドルチャレンジの3回目にして最後の決闘です。タイブレーカーです。

これは、Minecraftの新しいバージョンですが、バージョン1.16で挑戦することにしました。私はゲームをクリアしようとしますが、Daquavisはそれを阻止しようとします。レースです。しかも超激戦で、多くのものが賭けられています。

Minecraftではなく、Water Rises、Minecraftではなく、Lava Rises、あるいはその他、そういった類のチャレンジではありません。これは、殺人鬼／暗殺者と戦うMinecraftのスピードラン／スピードランナーです。

#MinecraftManhunt

hi.title: Minecraft स्पीडरनर बनाम $100,000 बाउंटी हंटर
hi.description:
दक्वाविस बनाम ड्रीम फाइनल। यह बिल्कुल पागलपन भरा था।

$7,000 मेडल प्रतियोगिता में भाग लें: https://pages.medal.tv/dream

मेरे सोशल मीडिया को फॉलो करें:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

मर्चेंडाइज: https://www.dreams.is

दक्वाविस: ​⁠@DaquavisMC

हमने इस सीरीज को Minecraft Manhunt नाम देने का फैसला किया। यह वीडियो इसका एक अलग संस्करण है, जिसमें एक शिकारी है और $100,000 दांव पर है।

यह हमारी $100,000 चुनौती में तीसरा और अंतिम द्वंद्व है। टाईब्रेकर।

यह एक नया Minecraft है, लेकिन, 1.16 चुनौती जिसे हमने आजमाने का फैसला किया है। मैं गेम को जीतने की कोशिश करता हूं, जबकि दक्वाविस मुझे रोकने की कोशिश करता है। यह एक दौड़ है, और यह बहुत तीव्र है, बहुत कुछ दांव पर लगा है।

Minecraft नहीं, बल्कि Water Rises या Minecraft नहीं, बल्कि Lava Rises, या कोई और चुनौती नहीं बल्कि ऐसी ही चुनौती। यह Minecraft का एक स्पीड रन / स्पीड रनर है जो एक हत्यारे / हत्यारे के खिलाफ है

#MinecraftManhunt

snippet.title: The Lavari Show EP 51 | Ft. Bhavya Gandhi | Pranks Lavari | The Comedy Factory
snippet.description:
Special Guest - Bhavya Gandhi 

Join us as we chat with Bhavya Gandhi, best known as Tapu from the iconic TV sitcom Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah (2008–2017), a role that made him a household name. After exiting the show, he transitioned to Gujarati cinema, starring in hit films like Pappa Tamne Nahi Samjaay, Bau Na Vichar, Kehvatlal Parivar, and the latest Ajab Raat Ni Gajab Vaat. He also made a Bollywood debut in Striker and appeared in Hindi TV and short films like Shaadi Ke Siyape and Pushpa Impossible. Hailing from a Gujarati Jain family and holding a B.Com from Mumbai University, Bhavya brings a unique cultural and educational perspective to our conversation. In this episode, we explore his journey from child star to regional cinema lead, his passion for music and direction, and what’s next on his creative horizon. 



Artists - 
Manan Desai, Om Bhatt, Deep Vaidya & Chirayu Mistry 

THE LAVARI SHOW - World Tour
Link - https://linktr.ee/mananmanan 

Directed by Chirayu Mistry & Dushyant Vyas
Camera Team - Seek Cinema Studios
Dushyant Vyas, Gaurav Gunjaria , Yash Akbari, Vishal Sharma, Neel Shah
Production Team : Pragnesh Rohit, Harshil Pandya 
Ahmedabad Production Team : Harshit Shah &  The Idea Bag team
Art Design - Sheel Thakore and Team
Makeup Artist - Parth Patel

snippet.title: सूजी मूंगदाल फरा नाश्ते के लिए परफेक्ट स्वाद सेहत सादगी नो फ्राई नो झंझट । Steamed Sooji Fara recipe
snippet.description:
तला-भुना छोड़िए,  खाइए ये स्टीम्ड और हेल्दी फरे, बिना झंझट वाला पौष्टिक नाश्ता,पारंपरिक स्वाद, बनाने में एकदम आसान, Sooji Fara Recipe – A Nutritious Start to Your Day,Low-Oil Breakfast – Sooji Fara with Protein-Rich Stuffing
#fara #breakfast #nashtha

Ingredients for Suji Moong Dal Fare
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1 cup (180 grams)

For Stuffing
मूंग धुली दाल - Moong dhuli dal - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1-2 tbsp


For Frying
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/4 tsp
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves 
तिल - Sesame - 1/2 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli 
नमक - Salt

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge?

#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Jab Tu Sajan | Aap Jaisa Koi | R. Madhavan, Fatima Sana Shaikh | Rochak Kohli,Mohit Chauhan,Gurpreet
snippet.description:
Tere bina main kya re,
Hun saanson se juda re!

For the love that soothes, binds, and grounds oneself – celebrate ‘forever waala pyaar’ with ‘Jab Tu Sajan’! Featuring R. Madhavan and Fatima Sana Shaikh, this beautiful romantic song is composed by Rochak Kohli, sung by Mohit Chauhan and penned by Gurpreet Saini. From the upcoming film ‘Aap Jaisa Koi’, this track promises to find a space in your heart just like that special one did!

#JabTuSajan #AapJaisaKoi #MohitChauhan #RMadhavan #FatimaSanaShaikh #RochakKohli #GurpreetSaini

Music Composer: Rochak Kohli
Lyricist: Gurpreet Saini
Singer: Mohit Chauhan
Music Producer: Rochak Kohli, Sharan Rawat
Guitar & Plucks: Mohit Dogra
Mix & Master: Eric Pillai
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor : Vasundhara Misra

Aap Jaisa Koi

Director: Vivek Soni
Producers: Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta, Somen Mishra
Banner Studio: Dharmatic Entertainment
Starring: R. Madhavan & Fatima Sana Shaikh
Streaming on Netflix 11th July

Lyrics:

Tere bina main kya re
Hun saanson se juda re
Ruan ruan hai tu
Bas tu
Piya

Hai rabb ki raza tu
Jo mujhko mila re
Hawaon sa sukoon
Hai tu
Piya

Tune mujhko pukara yun
Main chala aya baahon mein
Katt jayein teri chaaon mein
Saare din yeh saari rattiyaan

Ke jab tu sajan mere paas hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Tu hi safar tu hi meri talaash hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan
Tu hai dua meri jo poori huyi
Main toota tara hun
Main pichle janam tera hi tha
Is janam bhi dobara rahoon

Ke jab tu sajan mere paas hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Ki tere sang laagi akhiyaan
Raatein hain kayi jaagi akhiyaan

Tujhi mein paya rabb ko maine
Ho gayi hain bairaagi akhiyaan

Ki tere sang laagi akhiyaan
Raatein hain kayi jaagi akhiyaan

Tujhi mein paya rabb ko maine
Ho gayi hain bairaagi akhiyaan

Ishq ki dhoop chehre pe
Chanke tere jo mehki hai
Jag rahi hain diwali si
Mere dil ki saari rattiyaan

Ke jab tu sajan mere paas hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Tu hi safar tu hi meri talaash hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Dhuan dhuan dhal gaya
Paani mein utar gaya
Jab se hai paya tujhe
Dil mein basaya tujhe

Nadiya nazaron mein tu
Ik hi hazaron mein tu
Khudse juda na karun
Kabhi main khudaya tujhe

Sajde sawabon mein
Ishq vaale khwaabon mein
Dheeme dheeme behta hai tu

Tu hai dua meri jo poori huyi
Main toota tara hun
Main pichle janam tera hi tha
Is janam bhi dobara rahoon

Ke jab tu sajan mere paas hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Tu hi safar tu hi meri talaash hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

Ke jab tu sajan mere paas hai
Kuch aur na chahein akhiyaan

एक समय महर्षि विश्वामित्र अपने आश्रम में अन्य ऋषि-मुनियों के साथ जनकल्याण के लिए यज्ञ कर रहे थे। आश्रम के ऊपर आकाश में विचरण कर रहे मायावी राक्षसों सुबाहु व मारीच को विश्वामित्र के द्वारा किया जा रहा यज्ञ पसंद नहीं आता है और वे दोनों जानवरों के माँस, हड्डियों और खून को हवन कुण्ड में डालकर उस यज्ञ को विध्वंस कर देते है। यज्ञ के नियमों के अनुसार विश्वामित्र क्रोध नहीं कर सकते थे, इसलिए चाह कर भी वह उन्हें श्राप भी नहीं दे पाए। अतः वह सहायता के लिए अयोध्या के राजा दशरथ के पास जाते है और जहाँ दशरथ उनका आतिथ्य सत्कार करते है। आतिथ्य सत्कार से प्रसन्न होकर विश्वामित्र दशरथ को अपने अयोध्या आने का उद्देश्य बताते है कि असुरों के उत्पात के कारण यज्ञ और आध्यात्मिक साधना पूरी नहीं हो पा रही है। लंका के राजा रावण के मायावी गुप्तचर सुबाहु और मारीच उनका कोई भी अनुष्ठान पूरा नहीं होने दे रहे है। अतः हमें अपना पुत्र राम दे दो, जिससे हमारी रक्षा का उपाय हो जाएगा। लेकिन दशरथ नन्हे से बालक राम की जगह असुरों का सामना स्वयं अपनी सेना के साथ करने के लिए कहते है। जिससे विश्वामित्र क्रोधित हो जाते है और कुलगुरु वशिष्ठ की ओर देखते हुए कहते है कि राजा दशरथ अभी तक राम के दिव्य तेज को नहीं देख पाए है, अतः आप ही इन्हें समझाए। वशिष्ठ जी दशरथ की शंकाओं का निवारण करते हुए कहते है कि राम का नाम धर्म और संस्कृति की पहचान बनेगा, इसलिए विश्वामित्र राम के कल्याण के लिए आए है। वशिष्ठ जी के द्वारा आश्वस्त किए जाने पर दशरथ अपने पुत्रों राम और लक्ष्मण को विश्वामित्र के साथ तपोवन में भेज देते है। राम और लक्ष्मण के संरक्षण में विश्वामित्र पुनः यज्ञ करना प्रारम्भ करते है, जिसे देख सुबाहु और मारीच पुनः यज्ञ को ध्वस्त करने का प्रयास करते है, लेकिन राम और लक्ष्मण के तीर उनका संहार कर देते है, सुबाहु उसी समय मर जाता है और मारीच घायल होकर समुद्र तट पर जाकर गिरता है।

"वेद-पुराणों और धार्मिक ग्रंथों के अनुसार परम ईश्वर श्री हरि ने समय-समय पर धर्म की हानि को रोकने और अधर्म के विनाश करने के लिए मानव रूप में अवतार लिया और मानव कल्याण के लिए धर्म की पुनःस्थापना की तथा साथ-साथ अपने भक्तों का उद्धार भी किया। क्योंकि अवतार लेने का उद्देश्य केवल अधर्मियों का विनाश करना ही नहीं होता था बल्कि जनमानस में ईश्वर के प्रति भक्ति और उनके विश्वास को दृढ़ करना भी था। भगवान श्री राम ने जब त्रेतायुग में अवतार लिया, तब उन्होंने केवल रावण का वध ही नहीं किया बल्कि इस अवतार के माध्यम से अपने अनेकों भक्तों का उद्धार भी किया। आपका प्रिय धार्मिक चैनल तिलक अपनी इस शृंखला में भगवान श्री राम के द्वारा किए अपने भक्तों के उद्धार की कथाओं को प्रस्तुत कर रहा है। भक्ति भाव से इनका आनन्द लीजिए और तिलक से जुड़े रहिए।


#tilak #ramayan #katha #uddharkatha #ramayanuddharkatha"

snippet.description:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: 14 കാരൻ  ബേസിൽ ജോസഫിൻ്റെ പഴയ അശ്വമേധം കുത്തി പൊക്കിയിട്ടുണ്ട് 😍😆| BASIL JOSEPH | Aswamedham old
snippet.description:
ബേസിൽ ജോസഫിന്റെ ആരും കാണാത്ത മുഖം | ബേസിലിന്റെ പഴയ  വീഡിയോ കുത്തിപൊക്കിയിട്ടുണ്ട്  | വയനാട്ടിലെ ആ കുഞ്ഞ്  പയ്യൻ ആണ് ഇന്നത്തെ ബേസിൽ ജോസഫ് | BASIL JOSEPH | TOVINO | MINNAL MURALI |
IN THIS INTERVIEW BASIL JOSEPH was only 14 .
 
Director of the movies Kunjiramayanam,Godha and Minnal Murali   | Actor in Jaya Jaya Jaya hai |  Maranamass, Ponman, Sookshmadarshini                                                                 
basil Joseph is An engineer by profession, a film maker by passion.                                                                                                                   #kairalitv #kairalinews 

Basil Joseph is an Indian film director and actor in Malayalam films. He received his secondary education at St. Joseph's English Higher Secondary School in Sultan Bathery, where he demonstrated his versatility as a student by actively participating in sports, choir, and drama.

During his time at the College of Engineering in Trivandrum, Basil  continued to develop his diverse interests through involvement in extracurricular activities and participation in competitions. After graduation, he began a successful career at Infosys, a leading software company.

While working at Infosys, Joseph made his first zero-budget short film, Priyamvadha Katharayano, a quirky love story, and was noticed by  Malayalam Film industry. He was only 22 then.

His passion for cinema led him to quit his job at Infosys and pursue a career as a full-time filmmaker and actor.

Basil Joseph started as an assistant director for Thira in 2013, and his first film as a director was Kunjiramayanam (2015) in 2015. 

The sports drama, Godha (2017), Minnal Murali (2021), was about India's first-ever rural superhero in the Malayalam industry. J

The year 2022 marked a turning point in Basil Joseph's career, as he became a top actor with the release of the dramedy film, Jaya Jaya Jaya Jaya Hey (2022). This film provided him with the big break he had been seeking and tackled a relevant social issue with a unique blend of humor and storytelling.

snippet.title: NED vs NEP | Scotland, Nepal, Netherlands T20I Tri-Series 2025 | 3 Super Overs In One Match 😱
snippet.description:
Three Super Overs :scream::popcorn: An absolutely historic T20 thriller unfolded as Netherlands posted 152/7, with Nidamanuru leading. Nepal, thanks to Rohit Paudel's 48 and Daniel Doram's 3 wickets, tied it at 152/8. The match spiraled into an unprecedented third Super Over, featuring heroics from Kushal Bhurtel, Max O'Dowd, and Michael Levitt. Ultimately, Zach Lion-Cachet's wickets and Levitt's winning six secured a dramatic Dutch victory!

snippet.title: Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
snippet.description:
Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
In just 59 seconds, everything changed. What began as a routine flight filled with excited families, first-time flyers, and last-minute goodbye texts, turned into an unthinkable tragedy. As AI 171 took off, some passengers were heading home, others off to summer vacations — none of them knowing it would be their final journey. This video reconstructs the flight moment by moment: from the unusual dip at 14 seconds, to the explosion at 30 seconds. No "landed safely" messages followed. Instead, chaos unfolded on the ground — hospitals overwhelmed, families waiting, lives shattered. Survivors speak: one missed the flight by just hours, another saved by traffic, one more who jumped. This is more than a crash; it’s a story of loss, fate, and the fragile seconds that change everything.
Emergency number 18005691444

snippet.title: GRILLED CHICKEN WINGS | Juicy BBQ Chicken Wings Grilled in Village | Smoky Charcoal Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
In this video, we prepare delicious grilled chicken wings using a traditional charcoal firewood grill in our village. The chicken wings are marinated with a homemade blend of spices, curd, and a hint of lemon for that perfect tang. Cooked slowly over glowing embers, every bite is juicy, smoky, and full of authentic BBQ flavor.

Watch as we roast the wings to golden perfection on skewers, turning them gently to prevent burning and retain moisture. The smoky aroma, the natural outdoor cooking, and the crispy edges come together to make this one of the best chicken recipes we'll ever try.

es-US.title: ALITAS DE POLLO A LA PLANCHA | Jugosas alitas de pollo BBQ a la parrilla en el pueblo | Receta de...
es-US.description:
En este video, preparamos deliciosas alitas de pollo a la parrilla en una parrilla de carbón tradicional de nuestro pueblo. Las alitas se marinan con una mezcla casera de especias, requesón y un toque de limón para lograr ese toque ácido perfecto. Cocinadas lentamente sobre brasas, cada bocado es jugoso, ahumado y lleno del auténtico sabor a barbacoa.

Mira cómo asamos las alitas hasta que quedan perfectamente doradas en brochetas, dándoles la vuelta con cuidado para evitar que se quemen y conservar la humedad. El aroma ahumado, la cocción natural al aire libre y los bordes crujientes se combinan para hacer de esta una de las mejores recetas de pollo que jamás hayamos probado.

it.title: ALI DI POLLO ALLA GRIGLIA | Ali di pollo succose al barbecue grigliate nel villaggio | Ricetta de...
it.description:
In questo video, prepariamo deliziose alette di pollo alla griglia utilizzando una tradizionale griglia a legna del nostro villaggio. Le alette di pollo sono marinate con una miscela fatta in casa di spezie, cagliata e un pizzico di limone per un sapore acidulo perfetto. Cotte lentamente sulla brace, ogni boccone è succoso, affumicato e ricco di autentico sapore barbecue.

Guardate come arrostiamo le alette fino a doratura perfetta su spiedini, girandole delicatamente per evitare che si brucino e mantenere l'umidità. L'aroma affumicato, la cottura naturale all'aperto e i bordi croccanti si uniscono per rendere questa una delle migliori ricette di pollo che proveremo mai.

de-DE.title: GEGRILLTE HÜHNCHENFLÜGEL | Saftige BBQ-Hähnchenflügel im Dorf gegrillt | Rezept für rauchiges Häh...
de-DE.description:
In diesem Video bereiten wir köstliche gegrillte Hähnchenflügel auf einem traditionellen Holzkohlegrill in unserem Dorf zu. Die Hähnchenflügel werden mit einer hausgemachten Gewürzmischung, Quark und einem Hauch Zitrone für den perfekten Geschmack mariniert. Langsam über glühender Glut gegart, ist jeder Bissen saftig, rauchig und voller authentischem BBQ-Geschmack.

Sehen Sie zu, wie wir die Flügel auf Spießen goldbraun braten und dabei vorsichtig wenden, um ein Anbrennen zu verhindern und die Feuchtigkeit zu erhalten. Das rauchige Aroma, das natürliche Garen im Freien und die knusprigen Ränder machen dieses Rezept zu einem der besten Hähnchenrezepte, die wir je probiert haben.

pl.title: GRILLOWANE SKRZYDEŁKA Z KURCZAKA | Soczyste skrzydełka z kurczaka BBQ grillowane w Village | Prze...
pl.description:
W tym filmie przygotowujemy pyszne grillowane skrzydełka kurczaka, używając tradycyjnego grilla węglowego opalanego drewnem w naszej wiosce. Skrzydełka kurczaka są marynowane w domowej mieszance przypraw, twarogu i odrobinie cytryny, aby uzyskać idealny smak. Powoli pieczone nad żarzącymi się węglami, każdy kęs jest soczysty, wędzony i pełen autentycznego smaku BBQ.

Zobacz, jak pieczemy skrzydełka do złotej perfekcji na szaszłykach, delikatnie je obracając, aby zapobiec przypaleniu i zachować wilgoć. Wędzony aromat, naturalne gotowanie na świeżym powietrzu i chrupiące brzegi łączą się, aby stworzyć jeden z najlepszych przepisów na kurczaka, jaki kiedykolwiek wypróbujemy.

fr-FR.title: AILES DE POULET GRILLÉES | Ailes de poulet juteuses grillées au barbecue | Recette de poulet fumé...
fr-FR.description:
Dans cette vidéo, nous préparons de délicieuses ailes de poulet grillées sur un gril traditionnel au charbon de bois de notre village. Les ailes sont marinées avec un mélange maison d'épices, du lait caillé et une touche de citron pour une acidité parfaite. Cuites lentement sur des braises incandescentes, chaque bouchée est juteuse, fumée et regorge d'une authentique saveur barbecue.

Regardez-nous rôtir les ailes jusqu'à ce qu'elles soient dorées à la perfection sur des brochettes, en les retournant délicatement pour éviter qu'elles ne brûlent et conserver leur moelleux. L'arôme fumé, la cuisson naturelle en plein air et le croustillant des bords s'associent pour faire de cette recette de poulet l'une des meilleures que nous ayons jamais goûtées.

hi.title: ग्रिल्ड चिकन विंग्स | रसदार BBQ चिकन विंग्स गांव में ग्रिल्ड | स्मोकी चारकोल चिकन रेसिपी
hi.description:
इस वीडियो में, हम अपने गांव में पारंपरिक चारकोल फायरवुड ग्रिल का उपयोग करके स्वादिष्ट ग्रिल्ड चिकन विंग्स तैयार करते हैं। चिकन विंग्स को मसालों, दही और नींबू के एक संकेत के साथ घर के बने मिश्रण के साथ मैरीनेट किया जाता है ताकि वह सही स्वाद ले सके। धीरे-धीरे जलते अंगारों पर पकाए जाने पर, हर निवाला रसदार, धुएँदार और प्रामाणिक BBQ स्वाद से भरा होता है।

देखिए कि हम पंखों को सुनहरा होने तक कैसे भूनते हैं, उन्हें जलने से बचाने और नमी बनाए रखने के लिए उन्हें धीरे-धीरे घुमाते हैं। धुएँदार सुगंध, प्राकृतिक आउटडोर खाना पकाने और कुरकुरे किनारे मिलकर इसे सबसे अच्छी चिकन रेसिपी में से एक बनाते हैं जिसे हम कभी भी आजमाएँगे।

pt-BR.title: ASAS DE FRANGO GRELHADAS | Asas de Frango Suculentas Grelhadas na Vila | Receita de Frango Defuma...
pt-BR.description:
Neste vídeo, preparamos deliciosas asas de frango grelhadas em uma tradicional churrasqueira a carvão a lenha em nossa vila. As asas de frango são marinadas com uma mistura caseira de especiarias, coalhada e um toque de limão para aquele sabor picante perfeito. Assadas lentamente sobre brasas, cada mordida é suculenta, defumada e repleta do autêntico sabor de churrasco.

Veja como assamos as asas até dourarem perfeitamente em espetos, virando-as delicadamente para evitar que queimem e reter a umidade. O aroma defumado, o cozimento natural ao ar livre e as bordas crocantes se unem para fazer desta uma das melhores receitas de frango que já experimentamos.

nl-NL.title: GEGRILDE KIPPENVLEUGELS | Sappige BBQ-kippenvleugels gegrild in Village | Recept voor gerookte ho...
nl-NL.description:
In deze video bereiden we heerlijke gegrilde kippenvleugels op een traditionele houtskoolgrill in ons dorp. De kippenvleugels worden gemarineerd met een zelfgemaakte mix van kruiden, wrongel en een vleugje citroen voor die perfecte pittigheid. Langzaam gegaard boven gloeiende kolen, is elke hap sappig, rokerig en vol authentieke BBQ-smaak.

Zie hoe we de vleugels goudbruin roosteren aan spiesjes, waarbij we ze voorzichtig omdraaien om aanbranden te voorkomen en de sappigheid te behouden. De rokerige geur, het natuurlijke buitengaren en de knapperige randjes zorgen er samen voor dat dit een van de beste kiprecepten is die we ooit zullen proberen.

ja.title: グリルチキンウィング | 村で焼くジューシーなBBQチキンウィング | スモーキーな炭火焼きチキンのレシピ
ja.description:
この動画では、村の伝統的な炭火焼きグリルを使って、美味しいグリルチキンウィングを作ります。チキンウィングは、自家製のスパイス、カード、そしてほんのりとしたレモンの風味をブレンドしたマリネ液に漬け込み、完璧な酸味を引き出しています。燃え盛る炭火でじっくりと焼き上げるチキンウィングは、一口ごとにジューシーでスモーキー、そして本格的なバーベキューの風味が広がります。

串に刺したチキンウィングを、焦げ付かないように優しくひっくり返し、黄金色になるまで焼き上げる様子をご覧ください。スモーキーな香り、自然なアウトドア調理、そしてカリカリの端が絶妙に調和し、これまで食べたチキンレシピの中でも最高の一品となっています。

id.title: SAYAP AYAM PANGGANG | Sayap Ayam Panggang Lezat di Desa | Resep Ayam Panggang Arang Asap
id.description:
Dalam video ini, kami menyiapkan sayap ayam panggang yang lezat menggunakan panggangan arang kayu bakar tradisional di desa kami. Sayap ayam direndam dengan campuran rempah-rempah, dadih, dan sedikit lemon buatan sendiri untuk rasa asam yang sempurna. Dimasak perlahan di atas bara api yang menyala, setiap gigitannya berair, berasap, dan penuh dengan cita rasa BBQ yang autentik.

Saksikan saat kami memanggang sayap hingga keemasan sempurna di tusuk sate, membaliknya dengan lembut agar tidak gosong dan mempertahankan kelembapan. Aroma berasap, masakan alami di luar ruangan, dan tepian yang renyah berpadu menjadikan ini salah satu resep ayam terbaik yang pernah kami coba.

ko.title: 구운 치킨 윙 | 마을에서 구운 육즙 가득한 바비큐 치킨 윙 | 스모키 숯불 치킨 레시피
ko.description:
이 영상에서는 저희 마을의 전통 숯불 장작 그릴을 이용해 맛있는 구운 닭 날개를 만드는 과정을 보여드립니다. 닭 날개는 수제 향신료와 커드, 그리고 완벽한 새콤함을 위해 레몬 향을 살짝 더해 재워둡니다. 활활 타오르는 숯불 위에서 천천히 구워내 한 입 한 입마다 육즙과 스모키한 풍미, 그리고 정통 바비큐 풍미가 가득합니다.

꼬치에 꽂아 황금빛으로 완벽하게 구워지는 닭 날개를 천천히 돌려가며 타지 않고 수분을 유지하는 과정을 지켜보세요. 훈제 향, 자연스러운 야외 조리, 그리고 바삭한 가장자리가 어우러져 저희가 평생 먹어본 최고의 치킨 레시피 중 하나가 탄생했습니다.
